I can help you.

862
00:43:02,430 --> 00:43:03,890
I'm the owner's daughter.

863
00:43:04,300 --> 00:43:05,330
No, thanks.

864
00:43:07,170 --> 00:43:08,400
I'm leaving.

865
00:43:22,600 --> 00:43:24,530
Why are you looking at me like that?

866
00:43:27,130 --> 00:43:28,970
You just watched her like that.

867
00:43:29,570 --> 00:43:30,670
How would I know?

868
00:43:31,270 --> 00:43:33,200
She looked like she was faking it.

869
00:43:33,200 --> 00:43:35,400
How could you do that? She's not me...

870
00:43:35,400 --> 00:43:37,270
How could you do such a thing?

871
00:43:37,270 --> 00:43:39,770
I forbid you to blame me for this.

872
00:43:40,970 --> 00:43:42,430
Anyone else can blame me,

873
00:43:43,170 --> 00:43:44,170
but not you.

874
00:43:44,170 --> 00:43:46,370
This was done for you,

875
00:43:52,630 --> 00:43:53,830
for your sake.

876
00:44:00,230 --> 00:44:01,570
You must remember,

877
00:44:04,500 --> 00:44:06,370
we're on the same side.

878
00:45:52,730 --> 00:45:54,600
Sir, why did you trip my dad?

879
00:45:54,600 --> 00:45:55,430
San Francisco Beauty Salon

880
00:45:55,430 --> 00:45:56,930
was just a barbershop.

881
00:45:56,930 --> 00:45:58,700
I don't think it can survive for long.

882
00:45:58,700 --> 00:46:00,100
Didn't I tell you to break up with her?

883
00:46:00,100 --> 00:46:02,360
I was going to break up with her tomorrow.

884
00:46:02,830 --> 00:46:03,630
Deng Weiyu,

885
00:46:03,630 --> 00:46:04,800
what's wrong with you today?

886
00:46:04,800 --> 00:46:06,000
Go away!

887
00:46:06,000 --> 00:46:08,570
I really hate you!

888
00:46:08,570 --> 00:46:10,230
Or should we just keep pretending?

889
00:46:10,230 --> 00:46:12,200
You're really pushing your luck.

890
00:46:12,200 --> 00:46:13,770
This way, the two of us

891
00:46:13,770 --> 00:46:14,930
will avoid trouble.

892
00:46:15,470 --> 00:46:17,130
Who is this person in the photo?

893
00:46:17,130 --> 00:46:18,370
She's holding a child.

894
00:46:18,370 --> 00:46:19,330
Where is she now?
